Every day
- morning and evening announcements
- personalized transit or weather alerts
- what's the mayor doing, what's city hall doing

Trend / investigative pieces
- how does New York City work?
- what power does the mayor really have?

Onboarding
- where do you live, work
- how do you get around?

Use cases
- daily announcements (am/pm)
- longer stories on sundays and weekday evenings
-- interviews, explainers, investigations, trends
- breaking news

Phase 1
- text-only news network

Phase 2
- social media news app with built-in profiles on day one and recommended connections and why

Phase 3 - community powered news

